<p>John and Dave are back, and ready to answer, inform, and cogitate all right in front of your &hellip; ears! Topics covered today include printing from Mail.app, safely deleting junk mail, backing up your calendar, and continuing to troubleshoot Lion&rsquo;s oddities. Also included is Dave&rsquo;s explanation of how he&rsquo;s running Quicken on Lion (thanks to VMWare 4.1) and more. Download today, press play, and enjoy and learn with your two favorite geeks!</p>
